FOREIGN RELATIONS -- VIETNAM; VIETNAM -- ARMED FORCES; MILITARY FORCE 
REDUCTIONS; UNITED STATES -- MILITARY AID -- CAMBODIA; QUAYLE, DAN 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
