WEST GERMANY; EUROPE -- DEFENSE; NORTH ATLANTIC TREATY ORGANIZATION; ENGLAND -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- WEST GERMANY; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- WEST 
