<P>
Photo, Pirates' Jose Lind (airborne) trips over Barry Bonds while going after 
blooper hit by Giants' Will Clark as R.J. Reynolds (23) puts on the brakes. 
Pirate shortstop Rafael Belliard (not pictured) made the catch. Associated 
Press 
</P>
