<P>
Damages Awarded in Suit on Honda ATV: Honda Motor Co. of Japan will appeal $5.9 
million in damages awarded to a Salem, Ore., man who was injured while riding a 
Honda three-wheel all-terrain vehicle, a spokesman said. A Multnomah County 
Circuit Court Jury awarded damages Friday for Karl Oberg, 24. Honda's 
all-terrain off-road vehicle has been banned from sale in the United States 
